sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant DEV as Developer
  participant GH  as GitHub<br/>main + v* tag
  participant GHA as GitHub Actions
  participant WIF as Workload Identity<br/>Federation
  participant AR  as Artifact Registry
  participant ARG as ArgoCD
  participant GKE as GKE · ecom ns

  DEV->>GH: git tag v8 && git push origin v8
  GH-->>GHA: webhook triggers ci.yml
  Note over GHA: build-and-push (matrix · 5 services)

  GHA->>WIF: GitHub OIDC token<br/>(repo-scoped attribute_condition)
  WIF-->>GHA: short-lived GCP access token<br/>(impersonates github-actions-ci SA)

  GHA->>AR: docker buildx build --push<br/>tags: v8 · short-sha · latest
  Note over GHA: ui-service smoke test:<br/>pull image · curl · assert<br/>Cache-Control + ?v=<sha>

  GHA->>GH: bump-manifests job<br/>rewrite k8s/*.yaml image: <short-sha><br/>commit + push to main

  GH-->>ARG: poll detects new revision
  ARG->>AR: pull pinned image SHAs
  ARG->>GKE: Server-Side Apply
  Note over GKE: PDBs respected · HPAs preserved<br/>NEG drains old endpoints<br/>topology spread enforced

  GKE-->>DEV: live at shop.nativeops.site<br/>(~3 minutes end-to-end)
